WEBVTT

00:04:29.840 --> 00:04:33.000
It involved me being
searched for contrabands,

00:04:34.680 --> 00:04:37.976
changed from my ordinary clothes

00:04:38.000 --> 00:04:39.896
to the prison uniform,

00:04:39.920 --> 00:04:42.600
forced to squat on the ground,

00:04:43.800 --> 00:04:46.280
a posture that I soon came to learn

00:04:47.080 --> 00:04:49.936
would form the routine

00:04:49.960 --> 00:04:52.440
of the thousands of searches,

00:04:53.200 --> 00:04:54.696
number counts,

00:04:54.720 --> 00:04:56.200
that lay ahead of me.

00:04:59.000 --> 00:05:00.480
The women told me,